data.description: Nested within the mountains with views all around. Perfect home for first time homeowners and investors. Hardwood floors throughout the home. Enjoy a large backyard with a deck for entertaining. The kitchen boasts a double oven and newer appliances. All appliances stay with the home, including washer and dryer. The home is minutes from schools and hiking trails. Come see it for yourself today!
